	(gr_text "Possible Improvements:\n - Decoupling Capacitors across power plane splits\n - Run Ansys sim. to double check\n - Add filters to ensure clean signal for Current Sensor & more...\n - Follow this guide: https://www.allpcb.com/blog/pcb-knowledge/splitting-power-planes-when-and-why-to-divide-your-pcbs-power.html\n - ENSURE A CONTINOUS GND PLANE (less noisy)\n - Reroute and optimize placements again"
